Plot.
In this sequel to Escape From Witch Mountain, Tia and Tony, teenage sister 
and brother who possess extraordinary powers, leave their safe refuge on 
witch mountain for a trip to Los Angeles (their transport ship lands in 
the Rose Bowl). Tony is kidnapped by the evil Dr. Gannon and his spinster 
partner Letha and brainwashed into helping Gannon and Letha commit various 
crimes. It's up to Tia and a gang of truant kids to rescue Tony and prevent 
a major disaster.
